How to create mongoDB
---------------------
1. Download MongoDB form A [link] (https://www.mongodb.org/downloads?_ga=1.31199997.315563070.1444726713#production)
2. Define in your global environment the root directory for mongoDB.
3. open cmd.
4. md /data
5. md /data/db
6. mongod.exe for mongoDB server
7. mongo.exe for mongo shell (client)
